title: Moore throws for 2 TDs, Cincinnati beats Miami 34-23
text:
> Florida Moore throws for 2 TDs, Cincinnati beats Miami 34-23 Cincinnati head coach Tommy Tuberville turns to watch fans storm the field as he is surrounded by security following a 34-23 win over Miami in an NCAA college football game, Thursday, Oct. 1, 2015, in Cincinnati.
